<item>
            <title>[LU-5004] Test failure on test suite sanity, subtest test_77b file compare failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5004</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for wangdi &amp;lt;di.wang@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/84d88c86-d313-11e3-8c68-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/84d88c86-d313-11e3-8c68-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_77b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;file compare failed&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/osc/lustre-OST0000-osc-ffff88007a2e0400/checksum_type=crc32: Invalid argument&lt;br/&gt;
error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/osc/lustre-OST0001-osc-ffff88007a2e0400/checksum_type=crc32: Invalid argument&lt;br/&gt;
error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/osc/lustre-OST0002-osc-ffff88007a2e0400/checksum_type=crc32: Invalid argument&lt;br/&gt;
error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/osc/lustre-OST0003-osc-ffff88007a2e0400/checksum_type=crc32: Invalid argument&lt;br/&gt;
error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/osc/lustre-OST0004-osc-ffff88007a2e0400/checksum_type=crc32: Invalid argument&lt;br/&gt;
error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/osc/lustre-OST0005-osc-ffff88007a2e0400/checksum_type=crc32: Invalid argument&lt;br/&gt;
error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/osc/lustre-OST0006-osc-ffff88007a2e0400/checksum_type=crc32: Invalid argument&lt;br/&gt;
set checksum type to crc32&lt;br/&gt;
fail_loc=0x80000408&lt;br/&gt;
/tmp/f77-temp /mnt/lustre/f77b.sanity differ: byte 1, line 1&lt;br/&gt;
 sanity test_77b: @@@@@@ FAIL: file compare failed &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 77b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
